<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        /* General Page Styling */
        body {
    background: url('/images/back.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 100vh;
}


        .dashboard-container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 1000px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Enlarged Description Box */
        .description {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #ddd;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 25px auto;
            text-align: justify;
            margin-top: 10%;
        }

        /* Cards Container */
        .cards-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: nowrap;
        }

        /* Individual Cards */
        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            width: 30%;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;
            margin-top: 4%;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 174, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .card h2 {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .card p {
            color: #bbb;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        /* Buttons */
        .card a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            color: #000;
            background: #00aaff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background 0.3s ease-in-out, transform 0.2s ease-in-out;
        }

        .card a:hover {
            background: #0088cc;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Logout Button */
        .card.logout a {
            background: #ff4444;
        }

        .card.logout a:hover {
            background: #cc0000;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="dashboard-container">
        <h1>Welcome, <%= username %>!</h1>

        <div class="description">
            <p>
                Our real estate platform provides a seamless way to **manage, list, and browse properties** with ease. Whether you're a homeowner looking to sell, a landlord renting out apartments, or a business listing commercial spaces, our platform simplifies the process. You can **add properties** by specifying key details such as **location, price, size, and features**. Once added, these listings are stored securely and can be accessed anytime via the **View Properties** section.
                <br><br>
                Our intuitive dashboard ensures you stay in control, making **property management efficient and hassle-free**. Searching for a new home or commercial space? Browse through **verified listings**, compare options, and find properties that match your requirements effortlessly. With a **modern interface, fast navigation, and powerful filtering**, our platform is designed for convenience.
                <br><br>
                Whether you're a first-time user or an experienced real estate professional, we provide a **smooth and secure experience**. Start adding properties today and **take charge of your real estate listings** with just a few clicks!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cards-container">
            <div class="card">
                <h2>Add Property</h2>
                <p>List a new property for sale or rent.</p>
                <a href="/properties/add">âž• Add</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <h2>View Properties</h2>
                <p>Browse available properties.</p>
                <a href="/properties/view">ðŸ‘€ View</a>
            </div>

            <div class="card logout">
                <h2>Logout</h2>
                <p>End your session and log out.</p>
                <a href="/logout">ðŸšª Logout</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
